title: Sonny Terry Licks for blues harmonica
description:
A SOURCEBOOK OF SONNY TERRY LICKS FOR BLUES HARMONICA by Tom Ball
Besides 70 famous licks from Sonny, the book gives you some quick harmonica lessons, info on Sonny's style, a discography with key chart, and a bibliography. Includes CD that demonstrates each lick. Note/tab. 47 pp. 




SEED THIS WHEN DONE, This release is EXTREMELY RARE And HARD to get
